<hr data-start="1280" data-end="1283">
<h3 data-start="1285" data-end="1319">✅ 2. <strong data-start="1294" data-end="1319">Backup MySQL Database</strong></h3>
<h4 data-start="1321" data-end="1346"><strong data-start="1326" data-end="1346">Using phpMyAdmin</strong></h4>
<ol data-start="1347" data-end="1537">
<li data-start="1347" data-end="1375">
<p data-start="1350" data-end="1375">Log in to <strong data-start="1360" data-end="1374">phpMyAdmin</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1376" data-end="1420">
<p data-start="1379" data-end="1420">Select your database from the left panel.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1421" data-end="1449">
<p data-start="1424" data-end="1449">Click the <strong data-start="1434" data-end="1444">Export</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1450" data-end="1492">
<p data-start="1453" data-end="1492">Choose <strong data-start="1460" data-end="1469">Quick</strong> and format as <strong data-start="1484" data-end="1491">SQL</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1493" data-end="1537">
<p data-start="1496" data-end="1537">Click <strong data-start="1502" data-end="1508">Go</strong> to download the <code data-start="1525" data-end="1531">.sql</code> file.</p>
</li>
</ol>
